Usage: create_ccopt_clock_tree_spec [-help] [-keep_all_sdc_clocks]
                                    [-views <analysis_view>+] [{-file <filename>} ] [ -file <filename> ]

-help                          # Prints out the command usage
-file <filename>               # write clock tree specification script file
                               # (string, optional)
-keep_all_sdc_clocks           # keep clocks and clock trees in 1:1
                               # correspondence if possible (bool, optional)
-views <analysis_view>+        # Restricts the report to the delay corners
                               # associated with the specified views
                               # ((analysis_view)+, optional)